	<texts id="2001">
		<paragraph indent="0" tabs="" style="normal" height="0" width="400" y="+6" x="12" type="text"><![CDATA[<TEXTFORMAT LEADING="2"><P ALIGN="LEFT"><FONT FACE="Verdana" SIZE="13" COLOR="#000000" LETTERSPACING="0" KERNING="0">You should be able to work out from the question asked, the statements and the categories that you are going to hear someone talking about cinema from the 1950s-onwards. You should also see that you are expected to listen and find out for which period of time each statement is true. Look at the different periods and think about how they might be expressed differently. What century or part of the century does each period refer to, for example?</FONT></P></TEXTFORMAT>]]></paragraph>
